originalText.text: Was a customer for a few years. My go to parking lot. During the pandemic made a reservation to see a friend for a safe dinner and being that I would be drinking got a hotel for the night. I arrived left my car and walked the few blocks to check into hotel and  called my friend. He was feeling sick. We cancelled our plans. The hotel was very accommodating cancelled my room no problem. Icon not so much. Even though my car was in the lot for less than an hour, they charged me for a whole night stay. I called and spoke with them and explained everything the next day, I would even take a credit for a future reservation. They still refused. They just lost my business.
